attributionInfo.brokerName: Keller Williams Realty Boston-Metro | Back Bay
Berkshire Hathaway HomeServices Commonwealth Real Estate

description: First floor, open plan condo located directly across the street from Moakley Park and Carson Beach. Featuring 2 spacious bedrooms, 2 full baths, large private patio and a deeded parking spot.  Layout includes a cherry kitchen with stainless steel appliances, entertaining sized living room and an inviting dining space.  Hardwood floors throughout the condo, in unit washer/dryer, central A/C, abundant closet space and gas heat.  The primary suite includes a spa like bathroom with a soaking tub and dual vanities. Both bedrooms have California closets that provide custom storage space.  The secondary bedroom can be used as an office, den or guest room.  Boston Proper, major highways, Andrew Square T stop, and the beach are all readily accessible.  Downtown Southie is just a walk away with great restaurants and lots of shopping. Truly a must-see property.  No conventional financing: condo is unwarrantable.  Original owner has enjoyed the condo for 24 years.  Moving to RI and ready to close.
